ul.li: Collectively, simulation elements define a simulation scenario. Ex: Global Datacenter Network simulation element represents the said scenario.
Default elements are sufficient for most cases.
For custom scenarios, first, the new simulation elements needs to be defined in the definition file. And then, a corresponding element handler needs to be defined.
